            "title": "機器人春晚引爆熱議！AI濃度比論文還高 拆解背後中台科技角力",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"機器人春晚引爆熱議！AI濃度比論文還高 拆解背後中台科技角力\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/jAAsSSE._3JmsXrmvTTV2w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-02/1548f470-0e19-11f1-99fd-b40fea58b32b\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">機器人春晚引爆熱議！AI濃度比論文還高 拆解背後中台科技角力</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
